Name: Image Steganography 1.5.1
Description:
In this update:

> New 'Feedback' feature
> New Installer (Auto update from previous versions may be affected)

*+NOTE: This version and all of the application releases from now on run on .NET 4.0!!! Please make sure that this is installed for the application to run correctly! .NET 4.0 can be downloaded [url:here|http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/en/details.aspx?FamilyID=9cfb2d51-5ff4-4491-b0e5-b386f32c0992&displaylang=en].+*

Name: Image Steganography 1.5
Description:
*+New Release - 1.5+*
The latest release LOADS of changes:
* *MAJOR* speed improvement for the 'Enlarge' algorithm
* New algorithm; 'Embed' - fast, and almost completely undetectable
* 'Capacity' feature - displays the data capacity for an image, and shows whether the data can be encoded
* Image Scaling - if the data capacity for the image is too small, the image can be resized to allow for more data
* Various Bug Fixes and UI improvements

The application doesn't require administrator privileges to install.

Name: Image Steganography 1.4.5.2
Description:
The Latest release of Image Steganography!

The application has a new Error Reporting System, which allows it to export Error Log, so that bugs can be fixed more efficiently.

For more information, please see [url:Documentation|http://imagesteganography.codeplex.com/documentation].

*Note: the update feature is a little unstable at the moment (it should still work), but will be fixed soon*

Please feel free to leave a comment.

Name: Image Steganography 1.4

For instructions and information, please see Documentation.
